abstract: The modern holiday classic from 1994 completes the longest ever trip to the top of the Billboard singles chart, thanks to a dedicated marketing plan and a surge on streaming services.
snippet: The modern holiday classic from 1994 completes the longest ever trip to the top of the Billboard singles chart, thanks to a dedicated marketing plan and a surge on streaming services.
lead_paragraph: For Mariah Carey, this year’s Christmas season started promptly on Halloween night, just as the clock struck 12 a.m. and the calendar rolled over into November.

abstract: Make someone roast chicken with mashed potatoes, caramelized carrots and pan gravy.
snippet: Make someone roast chicken with mashed potatoes, caramelized carrots and pan gravy.
lead_paragraph: Good morning. The news is menacing these days. Irritation and mistrust dog at those who would like nothing more than to be celebrating unreservedly with family and friends this time of year: Christmas, African heritage, the Jewish festival of lights, the end of the year. The front page is scary, though. Social media is a neurotoxin. They are shouting on TV.

abstract: With President Donald Trump's impeachment trial looming in January, the five Democratic senators running against him are weighing tele-townhalls, quick trips and candidate proxies to keep their White House bids going while they serve as jurors.
snippet: With President Donald Trump's impeachment trial looming in January, the five Democratic senators running against him are weighing tele-townhalls, quick trips and candidate proxies to keep their White House bids going while they serve as jurors.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — With President Donald Trump's impeachment trial looming in January, the five Democratic senators running against him are weighing tele-townhalls, quick trips and candidate proxies to keep their White House bids going while they serve as jurors.
headline_main: January Juggle: Senators in 2020 White House Race to Balance Impeachment, Campaigning
headline_print_headline: January Juggle: Senators in 2020 White House Race to Balance Impeachment, Campaigning

abstract: The mayor of Alabama’s largest city is endorsing Joe Biden for the 2020 Democratic Party presidential nomination just weeks after the vice president met with a group of Southern black mayors representing millions of voters in key early primary states.

abstract: Tide Pod shout-outs onscreen. Flirtatious exchanges with companies on Twitter. Netflix may not run ads, but it has become a coveted marketing platform.
snippet: Tide Pod shout-outs onscreen. Flirtatious exchanges with companies on Twitter. Netflix may not run ads, but it has become a coveted marketing platform.
lead_paragraph: Netflix subscribers like being able to glide through entire seasons of “Stranger Things” and “The Crown” without sitting through commercials for insurance and S.U.V.s with bows on the hood. Subscriptions, rather than advertising, drive its nearly $16 billion in annual revenue, and being commercial-free “remains a deep part of our brand proposition,” Netflix said in a statement.
